thread.title: Keven Ann
thread.title_full: Kiwi Sheepskins reviewed by Keven Ann

author: Keven Ann
title: Keven Ann
text:
I've ordered sheepskins, lamb skins, boots, and various medical sheepskin products. Orders are quickly delivered to the US, clean and well packaged. I can ship to a friend as a gift. Website has always worked flawlessly and has improved dramatically in appearance recently.
Really nice products, truthfully described, good prices.
Thank you.
